20:09.374 --> 20:12.678
She's right.
You need something alive.

20:15.681 --> 20:17.315
Go to sleep, both of you.

20:17.348 --> 20:19.685
Something sensational.

20:20.318 --> 20:21.887
That's a big word.

20:21.920 --> 20:24.089
It's your word.

20:24.122 --> 20:27.092
Something that isn't stuffed.

20:27.125 --> 20:29.628
- Like a mermaid.
- Or a unicorn.

20:30.996 --> 20:33.298
Unicorns aren't real.

20:33.331 --> 20:35.801
Well, mermaids
aren't real either.

21:02.327 --> 21:04.362
You must be Gertrude Stratton.

21:04.395 --> 21:05.664
I'm looking for your son.

21:06.431 --> 21:07.766
I don't have a son.

21:08.466 --> 21:10.068
The hospital record says you do.

21:10.101 --> 21:12.538
Charles, right? Age 22?

21:17.275 --> 21:18.777
Charles!

21:20.278 --> 21:21.479
Charles!

21:35.326 --> 21:36.895
P.T. Barnum, at your service.

21:38.530 --> 21:40.866
I am putting together a show

21:40.899 --> 21:42.133
and I need a star.

21:43.268 --> 21:45.336
You want people
to laugh at me.

21:45.370 --> 21:46.681
Well, they're laughing
anyway, kid,

21:46.705 --> 21:47.973
so might as well get paid.

21:57.382 --> 21:59.417
I see a soldier,
no, a general

21:59.450 --> 22:02.921
riding across the stage
with a sword and a gun,

22:02.954 --> 22:04.522
and... and...

22:04.556 --> 22:07.058
and the most beautiful uniform
ever made.

22:07.092 --> 22:08.960
People will come
from all over the world,

22:08.994 --> 22:11.963
and when they see him,
they won't laugh.

22:17.168 --> 22:18.837
They'll salute.

22:34.720 --> 22:35.987
How's it looking, girls?

22:42.661 --> 22:44.495
Hey! You looking for freaks?

22:44.529 --> 22:46.331
I know where
you can find one of them.

22:47.532 --> 22:48.734
Really?

22:53.104 --> 22:54.706
Come on, girls.

22:59.044 --> 22:59.911
Hello.

22:59.945 --> 23:01.146
Sir, you shouldn't
be here.

23:01.179 --> 23:03.148
I'm sorry,
who's doing that singing?

23:06.217 --> 23:08.553
It's you, isn't it?

23:08.586 --> 23:10.488
Sir, I'll have
to ask you to leave.

23:10.521 --> 23:12.357
You are so talented, blessed...

23:15.093 --> 23:16.361
Extraordinary.

23:17.629 --> 23:19.230
Unique.

23:20.431 --> 23:22.233
I would even say beautiful.

23:24.502 --> 23:25.871
Sir.

23:26.537 --> 23:28.606
Please leave me alone.

23:35.947 --> 23:37.983
They don't understand,
but they will.

23:52.330 --> 23:53.665
This line is so...

23:53.699 --> 23:57.368
Oh, my God! Oh, goodness.

