24:52.457 --> 24:54.225
What is your name?

24:54.259 --> 24:56.728
Vasily Palvos, sir.

24:56.762 --> 24:58.329
Yeah, we're gonna
change that name.

24:58.363 --> 25:00.866
Uh, I think you're Irish.

25:02.533 --> 25:04.202
We have a show!

25:05.837 --> 25:08.306
