44:49.219 --> 44:50.955
Who's that?

44:50.988 --> 44:52.889
The opera singer?

44:53.557 --> 44:54.891
Singer, huh?

44:56.026 --> 44:59.063
She's the most famous performer
in all of Europe.

44:59.096 --> 45:01.765
She's sold out
La Scala a dozen times.

45:01.798 --> 45:04.334
