She's a person.

45:24.688 --> 45:26.090
Miss Lind.

45:26.790 --> 45:28.525
My name is Phillip Carlyle.

45:30.494 --> 45:33.463
And this extraordinary gentleman
next to me...

45:33.497 --> 45:34.965
Phineas Taylor Barnum.

45:34.999 --> 45:36.100
The pleasure's mine.

45:36.133 --> 45:37.401
