all the way over here

45:42.706 --> 45:44.741
I must be doing something right.

45:44.774 --> 45:47.111
That, or something very wrong.

45:47.144 --> 45:50.014
Well, in the world of publicity,
there's hardly a difference.

45:50.047 --> 45:53.250
I believe those are the words
of a scoundrel, Mr. Barnum.

45:53.283 --> 45:56.086
A showman, Miss Lind,
just a showman.

45:56.120 --> 45:58.355
The best on my side
of the Atlantic.

45:58.388 --> 46:00.790
Well, if you do
say so yourself.

46:00.824 --> 46:04.028
I do, but I don't have to.

46:04.061 --> 46:05.095
- Oh, no. No.
- Right?

46:05.129 --> 46:07.097
No, he is one of the best.

46:07.131 --> 46:09.133
Oh, that's very kind of you.
Miss Lind...

46:09.166 --> 46:10.300
