01:13:40.015 --> 01:13:43.518
♪ These hands
could hold the world ♪

01:13:43.551 --> 01:13:48.223
♪ But it'll never be enough ♪

01:13:49.291 --> 01:13:52.828
♪ Never be enough ♪

01:14:30.665 --> 01:14:32.067
