01:14:37.405 --> 01:14:39.607
What was that?

01:14:39.641 --> 01:14:41.877
That was goodbye.

01:14:47.115 --> 01:14:48.860
Hey, thank you
very much for coming.

01:14:48.884 --> 01:14:50.762
- Tell your friends and neighbors!
- What a wonderful show!

01:14:50.786 --> 01:14:52.888
